{"tid":2376844,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"華迪腹部做手術預唞1個月 李城未來4場缺王牌射手","createTime":"2021-01-23T06:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T07:43:14.000Z","uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"763e8c7d35ebbeed77fe42ca2f0584ff2d31840b","tid":2376844,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T06:09:03.000Z","msg":"據英國傳媒周五報道，英超李斯特城王牌射手占美華迪因需為腹部施行小型手術，預料將要養傷數周時間，會過錯本周的英足盃賽事及未來數場聯賽。<br />\n<br />\n34歲的華迪季初即表現大勇，開季後18場聯賽交出11個入球和5個助攻，帶領「銀狐」於19輪英超後排在第3位。可是，李城接下數周將要缺少這位王牌射手，這位英格蘭射手因腹部有疝氣（器官向外形成肚皮有位置明顯突出）需做手術，預料要養傷幾周。李城領隊羅渣士周五在記者會上就確認消息：「占美華迪將休戰數周。我們這幾個月以來一直小心看管着他，他表現都很出色。現在他將要在腹部位置接受手術，然後便會歸隊。」<br />\n<br />\n這意味着華迪將無緣本周的英足盃第四圈鬥英冠賓福特的賽事，也很大機會缺陣李城接下四場鬥愛華頓、列斯聯、富咸和狼隊的聯賽。羅渣士又透露，在華迪缺陣期間，有機會由西班牙前鋒艾約斯佩雷斯頂替其位置：「我們之前也曾在華迪缺陣下入球和勝出比賽，過去數周即使他沒入球時，也為球隊帶來貢獻。佩雷斯雖沒華迪那麼快及大影響力，但他也是個出色的射手，我還有（尼日利亞前鋒）伊恩拿祖也能帶來威脅。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20210122/B5UAKQJDOZGYNM3FX24IBBVC3M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20210122%2FB5UAKQJDOZGYNM3FX24IBBVC3M%2F&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5B0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=c094cdba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20210122%2FB5UAKQJDOZGYNM3FX24IBBVC3M%2F&h=fa7200b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20210122/B5UAKQJDOZGYNM3FX24IBBVC3M/</a>"},{"pid":"0e38f93eecf3058fb2a395caa12f989f9f8d5de8","tid":2376844,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T06:52:37.000Z","msg":"李城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0abcb058a9eac3d42e90b47dd9b0c7495da349a3","tid":2376844,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T06:54:19.000Z","msg":"李斯贏整體規律<br />\n未必睇到悲觀"},{"pid":"f787847bcced64e0b369c81a4b0ad1644069ba3b","tid":2376844,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T06:56:55.000Z","msg":"佩雷斯聽個名都知猛料"},{"pid":"0613ea37b62a7eee99cb387574fb5f94cfa78239","tid":2376844,"uid":19093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:19:59.000Z","msg":"華D,早日康復"},{"pid":"2e816ee4370ce478cf82dd96118663e30facc1ba","tid":2376844,"uid":8636,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:28:13.000Z","msg":"痢事春秋 快撚啲開post話天助曼聯啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efbef12760663b5e0b0df782790d948abde45a5","tid":2376844,"uid":25771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0abcb058a9eac3d42e90b47dd9b0c7495da349a3","tid":2376844,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T06:54:19.000Z","msg":"李斯贏整體規律<br />\n未必睇到悲觀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T07:43:14.000Z","msg":"無華迪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你咪靠伊恩拿祖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一季入兩三球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}